node.text:
🎁 Metal Poster + $100x3 Giveaway 🎁
Our audio picture Instagram series BornWild • Versus just launched!
To celebrate, we're doing a giveaway of 3x Metal Posters + $100 (three winners).
 All you have to do to enter is:

✅ Screenshot your favorite picture
✅ Crop & Repost in a Story
✅ Tag @ogzone & tell us what you like about the series
✅ Follow @ogzone

Multiple Story reposts are okay as long as it's once a day.

Ends: 8/25 at 5 pm (EST)

We will randomly pick three winners at random hours between August 11th & August 25th. They will be announced on August 26th on @ogzone. 
The $100 will be distributed via PayPal directly to each winner. The metal posters will be sent within three weeks after receiving all elements necessary.

We will contact the winners via our official account. Do not accept follow requests from fake accounts and do not provide them any personal or credit card information.

Good luck!
.
.
.
.
.
#contest #giveaway

node.text:
@blowcreation 10K & The Kriminal World [A Cigarette's Time] comic & figure crowdfunding campaign will be launch on 10 August at Kickstarter. 
 
First 48 hours early bird special available! 
 
** Visit the landing page for details of the campaign (Link in bio👆) 
 
https://www.blowcreation.com/kickstarter 
 
About the comic: 
 
In the great gang-infested city of 'Kriminal World', a highly secretive operation known as [Project 10K] has surfaced from its dark underbelly. Rumor has it that [Project 10K} is a 'weapon' of sorts created for the purpose of eradicating every gang in the city. Naturally, most gangs within Kriminal World placed a dead or alive contract on any who's associated with [Project 10K]. 
​ 
Here today, two super soldiers bred from [Project 10K] - Zeus and Poseidon, appear in an industrial district, where one of them needs to complete a highly dangerous mission before the other finishes a cigarette. 
​ 
[A Cigarette's Time] is but one of many stories from the ever-expanding universe of 10K & The Kriminal World that we have conceived over several years. More single-issue comic books featuring stories surrounding the wide array of 10K heroes can be readily released, if we are successful in gathering the help and support that we need from all of you, our classy patrons. 
​ 
About the figure: 
 
Asides from being one of the Mob's ace hitmen, no one knows anything about Zeus and his former life, let alone how his past is deeply connected with the beginnings of the mysterious [Project 10K] 
​ 
Over the last several months, we have hoped that one day we can bring our 10K & The Kriminal World cast to life from their 2D plane. It only made sense that for this very special and limited collectible, we chose Zeus - everyone's favorite main character. 
​ 
To express our gratitude for this first round of support from you, we wanted to give you something truly unique. Which is why for this particular collectible, we decided to let go of Zeus' original color scheme, and went with a more stylized version with a black and electroplated gold combination for this collectible Figurine. 
 
#10KComics #Project10K #Kriminalworld #comics #gangsters #blowcreation #crowdfund
